{"tid":1044622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太尷尬！港區人大陳勇鬧錯國家 英國無端替美國捱轟3分鐘","createTime":"2019-03-03T04:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T07:19:17.000Z","uid":153236,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d8072ec127f3a50b3fcc2679779ebaebfdfb9a11","tid":1044622,"uid":153236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/125331_c1da9439f02937687120488e76181f14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F125331_c1da9439f02937687120488e76181f14.png&h=93f9267d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地兩會三月開幕，一班港區人大政協陸續上京接旨，美國駐港總領事唐偉康最近相當勇猛，做完電視台再公開致辭，話擔心中央侵蝕香港嘅高度自治，影響營商環境，又話近年香港經常重「一國」輕「兩制」，搞到外交部駐港特派員公署要向美領館提出嚴正交涉，今日離港上京嘅港區人大代表陳勇都鬧埋一份，佢向記者鬧足三分幾鐘，高喊「英國」要向香港人同全國人民道歉！<br />\n<br />\n陳勇義正辭嚴鬧爆「英國駐港總領事」近日嘅言論，佢絕非一時搞錯「美國」做「英國」，佢係連續三分鐘力數英國嘅不是，仲話英國歷任首相對香港嘅一國兩制評價好高，連蘇格蘭、愛爾蘭嘅領袖都提出要效法一國兩制，解決英倫三島嘅紛爭、脫歐嘅問題：「作為一個英國嘅外交官，更多應該為佢自己嘅祖國更多貢獻！」之後仲樂此不疲咁樣力數英國國內面對嘅問題，英國都唔會想外國干預。<br />\n<br />\n陳勇到咗北京後，知道自己衰咗，就向傳媒指自己頭先喺香港「講錯咗」，搞錯咗英國同美國，故佢正式向英國駐港總領事道歉，仲話自己講錯嘢都會道歉，所以美國（佢終於講啱）駐港總領事都應該學佢咁，就自己不當言論公開向全港市民同全國人民道歉喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190302/59322259\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190302%2F59322259&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyELccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=dcc3e3a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190302%2F59322259&h=de743e54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190302/59322259</a>"},{"pid":"a4440646e8af6ff7fdd0b8118e9143225bf3346f","tid":1044622,"uid":39974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed285cf4e151e86f9bc6b2003a983e47bc3f7271","tid":1044622,"uid":160561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13775ded1b2c7341e00dba9a6d3da22028a61dd3","tid":1044622,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"呢條友，成日鳩up，柒咗扮無嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2121490916f0b5a2de860372b65a7a6806c014","tid":1044622,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"柒到唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ce16a66afadb030a0f302f1c32e6a16ae1a5d2","tid":1044622,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"柒過關家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad372500b750cadb5d11526a69ca26e6cd966f4","tid":1044622,"uid":121580,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/142410_1678956968fd86dee182faefdda7a6c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F142410_1678956968fd86dee182faefdda7a6c5.jpg&h=f9796260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立即開除<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee10f7fef03e38b78799e49fc01c3f01e045644","tid":1044622,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"講得好<br />\n將香港交比共產政權應該道歉"},{"pid":"6c607565cc4bf913e98f9978245eda258a04511b","tid":1044622,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-